See https://github.com/eitanyaffe/hpipe for complete instructions.

System files:
- project_id: unique identifier of project
- user_vars: Customize various user-defined parameters
- path_vars: Customize input, output and external tool paths

Experimental design files:
- basic.cfg:
  Input: Shotgun and Hi-C libraries
- skip_assembly.cfg: 
  Input: Assembly and Hi-C library

